Risperidone
===========

Roblox game test playground.

Prerequisite
------------

Required for external Roblox development:

    - aftman <https://github.com/LPGhatguy/aftman>
    - rojo <https://github.com/rojo-rbx/rojo>

Installation
------------

You only need to do this only once:

    aftman install

Synchronize
-----------

To get the latest Workspace (map):

    lune run scripts/sync.luau

Spawn a rojo server:

    rojo serve

Then connect to the server from Roblox Studio <https://rojo.space/docs/v7/getting-started/installation/#installing-the-plugin>.
